      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "LOS ANGELES, April 6.-What\nthreatens to be one of the most\ndisastrous fires in the history of\nthe city broke out this afternoon\non the third floor of the wholesale\npaper warehouse of A. Zellerbach\n& Sons. All houses in the vicinity\nare threatened.\n\n\nCornered by flames, four firemen\nsaved their lives by crawling down\nq vent pipe."
    }
